	<td bgcolor="3c6450" width="100%" valign="top">
	<font face="arial" size="0"> <b>Application process</b></font>
	<p><font face="arial" size="2"><font size="4">GENERAL REQUIREMENTS</font> <br />
<br />
- Level 60 <br />
- Melee: Epic or better. For casters if you don't have it don't expect us to get it for you. <br />
- Be able to get every resist (unbuffed!) 100+ <br />
- Innate Run Speed 3 (SoL skills) <br />
- In-and Outdoor insta-click items: The more the merrier. <br />
- Solid connection, if you go linkdead a lot don't bother. And ofcourse a stable comp. <br />
- Being able to raid from 5 PM GMT +1 untill 12 PM GMT +1 <br />
- Sebilis, Skyshrine key. <br />
- Sponsor. Every person that apply's and wants to be accepted has to have 1 sponsor at minimum. <br />
<br />
<br />
All applications that don't meet the requirements will be ignored. If you are not sure and think you're "special", contact me (Tual) in-game or email me at <a href="mailto:fibe@fibe.net">fibe@fibe.net</a> <br />
<br />
-------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------<br />
<font size="4">RECRUITMENT STATUS</font> <br />
<br />
Following Classes are closed for Recruitment:<br />
<br />
Cleric - Closed<br />
Bards - Closed<br />
Beastlord - Closed<br />
Enchanter - Closed<br />
Magicians - Closed<br />
Necromancer - closed <br />
Paladins - Closed<br />
Rangers - Closed<br />
Shadowknights - Closed <br />
Shaman - Closed<br />
Warriors - Closed<br />
Rogues - Closed<br />
<br />
Following classes are open for Recruitment:<br />
<br />
Druid - Open<br />
Monks - Open<br />
Wizards - Open<br />
--------------------------------------------------<br />
<font size="4">APPLICATION FORM</font> <br />
<br />
The the answers to the following questions, need to be send to <a href="mailto:fibe@fibe.net">fibe@fibe.net</a>.<br />
<br />
-Character name <br />
-email <br />
-class <br />
-race <br />
-amount of AA points <br />
-keys you own <br />
<br />
-Previous and current guild( if any) <br />
-Why are you leaving your current guild ? <br />
-How long have you been in it ? <br />
<br />
-Give a full description of any twinks <br />
<br />
-Why Mortalis? <br />
-What do you think you have to offer us ? <br />
<br />
-Link to Magelo profile: If you don't have one make it <a href="http://www.magelo.com" target="_blank">here</a>.<br />
<br />
<br />
-Tradeskills <br />
<br />
-Average play hours during week & weekend. And how many days/week do you play. <br />
<br />
-Please list the High end mobs you have killed and zones visited. <br />
<br />
-Played time ("/played") <br />
<br />
<br />
-Who is/are your sponsor(s) <br />
<br />
And most important:<br />
<br />
<br />
<font size="4">Don't contact us, we'll contact you !</font></font></p>
	
	<p><p><font face="arial" size="2">__________________<br>
